Package it.polimi.ingsw.events.servertoclient

Interface EventToClientVisitor

All Known Implementing Classes:
EventHandlerCLI, EventHandlerGUI
public interface EventToClientVisitor
This interface contains the list of the event that the client could receive from the server. This interface uses the overloading of the method to accept events.
Author:
Stefano Fossati
